This is FILEUTIL version 0.20 (Jan. 2002)
written by Dominique B‚r‚ziat (c) 2002

Goal

It is a LDG module providing shell functions to
copy, move and delete files and subfolders. This
version support now long filename. The module
provides too equivalent of GEMDOS functions FsFisrt(),
FsNext(), FsetDta() and FgetDta() supporting
long filename.

Install

Just copy GEMSYS/LDG/FILEUTIL.LDG in your LDG folder.
The file INCLUDE/LDG/FILEUTIL.H containt the interface
to FILEUTIL functions.
Documentation is the file MAN/CAT3L/FILEUTIL.3L

Contact

